<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SAMBAT! - Layanan Aspirasi dan Pengaduan Online Rakyat</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #c41e3a;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin: 0 15px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            color: #c41e3a;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #c41e3a;
        }

        .navbar .menu {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar .menu button {
            background: #c41e3a;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-left: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .navbar .menu button:hover {
            background: #a71d2a;
        }

        .form-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .form-title {
            background: #c41e3a;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: -40px -40px 30px -40px;
            border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .form-title h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .classification {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .classification h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .radio-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .radio-option {
            flex: 1;
            border: 2px solid #c41e3a;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #c41e3a;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .radio-option:hover {
            background: #f8d7da;
        }

        .radio-option input[type="radio"] {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .radio-option input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
            background: #c41e3a;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .radio-option label {
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .notice {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #666;
            position: relative;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .notice .help-icon {
            margin-left: 10px;
            background: #c41e3a;
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
        }

        .tooltip {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 30px;
            left: 10px;
            background: white;
            color: #333;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            z-index: 10;
            width: 250px;
        }

        .help-icon:hover .tooltip {
            display: block;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            border-color: #c41e3a;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            height: 150px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        ::placeholder {
            color: #999;
        }

        .privacy-options {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .privacy-options label {
            margin-right: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .privacy-options input {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: #c41e3a;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            background: #a71d2a;
        }

        .step-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .step {
            text-align: center;
            width: 18%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #c41e3a;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .step h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .step:after {
            content: '';
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #ccc;
            position: absolute;
            top: 30px;
            left: 80px;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .step:last-child:after {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .navbar .menu {
                margin-top: 15px;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            .navbar .menu button {
                margin-top: 10px;
                margin-left: 10;
            }

            .radio-group {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .radio-option {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .step-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .step {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .step:after {
                display: none;
            }
        }

        .navbar .menu button + button {
    margin-left: 10px;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">SAMBAT!</div>
        <div class="menu">
            <a href="/sambat">Tentang SAMBAT!</a>
            <a href="/laporan">Laporan Publik</a>
           <a href="/login"> <button>Masuk</button></a>
            <a href="/register"><button>Daftar</button></a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Layanan Aspirasi dan Pengaduan Online Rakyat</h1>
            <p>Sampaikan laporan Anda langsung kepada instansi pemerintah berwenang</p>
        </div>

        <div class="form-container">
            <div class="form-title">
                <h2>Sampaikan Laporan Anda</h2>
            </div>
            <form action="/login" method="GET">
            <form id="laporanForm">
                <div class="classification">
                    <h3>Pilih Klasifikasi Laporan</h3>
                    <div class="radio-group">
                        <div class="radio-option">
                            <input type="radio" id="pengaduan" name="klasifikasi" value="PENGADUAN">
                            <label for="pengaduan">PENGADUAN</label>
                        </div>
                        
                        
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="notice">
                    <span>Perhatikan Cara Menyampaikan Pengaduan Yang Baik dan Benar</span>
                    <div class="help-icon">
                        ?
                        <div class="tooltip">Pastikan laporan disampaikan dengan jelas, detail, dan sopan. Sertakan bukti pendukung jika ada.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <form action="/login" method="POST">

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="judullaporan">Ketik Judul Laporan Anda</label>
                    <input type="text" id="judullaporan" placeholder="Contoh: Pelayanan Buruk di Kantor Kecamatan" >
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="isi">Ketik Isi Laporan Anda</label>
                    <textarea id="isi" placeholder="Jelaskan secara detail laporan Anda..." ></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="tanggal">Tanggal Kejadian</label>
                    <input type="date" id="tanggal" >
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="lokasi">TKP (Tempat Kejadian Perkara)</label>
                    <input type="text" id="lokasi" placeholder="Contoh: Kantor Kecamatan Sukajadi, Jl. Raya No. 123" >
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="category-select">Pilih Kategori:</label>
                    <select id="category-select" name="category-select" >
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Pilih Kategori</option>
                        <option value="Infrastruktur">Infrastruktur</option>
                        <option value="Pelayanan Publik">Pelayanan Publik</option>
                        <option value="Lingkungan">Lingkungan</option>
                        <option value="Lainnya">Lainnya</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="image-upload">Unggah Gambar:</label>
                    <input type="file" id="image-upload" name="image-upload" accept="image/*">
                </div>
                
                        
                <div class="privacy-options">
                    <label>Opsi Privasi:</label>
                    <div class="radio-group">
                        <input type="radio" id="anonim" name="privacy" value="Anonim">
                        <label for="anonim">Anonim</label>
                        <input type="radio" id="rahasia" name="privacy" value="Rahasia" checked>
                        <label for="rahasia">Rahasia</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Kirim Laporan</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-container">
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">✍️</div>
            <h3>Tulis Laporan</h3>
            <p>Laporkan keluhan atau aspirasi anda dengan jelas dan lengkap</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">✅</div>
            <h3>Proses Verifikasi</h3>
            <p>Dalam 3 hari, laporan Anda akan diverifikasi dan diteruskan ke instansi berwenang</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">🔄</div>
            <h3>Proses Tindak Lanjut</h3>
            <p>Dalam 5 hari, instansi akan menindaklanjuti dan membalas laporan Anda</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">💬</div>
            <h3>Beri Tanggapan</h3>
            <p>Anda dapat menanggapi kembali balasan yang diberikan dalam waktu 10 hari</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-icon">✔️</div>
            <h3>Selesai</h3>
            <p>Laporan Anda akan terus ditindaklanjuti hingga terselesaikan</p>
        </div>
    </div>

   

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>Copyright by Kelompok 7</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>